            <li class="font-normal text-base lg:text-lg text-[#595959]"><em class="text-[#20265a]">Fractional Ownership:</em> According to Morgan Stanley, tokenization facilitates fractional ownership, broadening access to a more diverse investor base and potentially increasing the global number of real estate investors by 10 folds.</li>
